data.description: 3 bed 1 bath ranch home on a .302 acre corner lot on the south side of Marshfield. This home is located near parks, schools, walking/biking trails and the fairgrounds. The home has lots of potential and includes the washer, dryer, refrigerator, microwave, along with an electric oven/range. There are hook ups for a gas oven/range if preferred. Schedule your private showing today!,Do not let dog and 2 cats out please.
